  "title": "Presales Solution Architect",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>• Collaborate with the sales team to identify customer needs.</p><p>• Design and propose cloud-based solutions that meet customer needs and align with their strategic goals.</p><p>• Develop and deliver presentations, demonstrations, and proof-of-concepts to showcase the value of proposed solutions.</p><p>• Provide technical leadership and guidance throughout the project lifecycle.</p><p>• Stay current with the latest cloud technologies, industry trends, and competitive</p><p>landscape.</p><p>• Build strong relations with customers, partners, and internal stakeholders.</p><p>• Assist in developing sales strategies and account plans to drive revenue growth.</p><p>• Participate in industry events, conference, and webinars to promote the company’s cloud solutions.</p><p>• Prepare and maintain technical documentation, including architecture diagrams, solution briefs, and customer proposals.</p><p>• Document customer interactions, solution designs, and feedback for internal use and continuous improvement.</p><p>• Conduct internal knowledge-sharing sessions to improve team capabilities.</p><p>• Any other ad-hoc duties assigned</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>• 3 years of experience in a presales role in the industry</p><p>• Experience in cloud-based deployment and management in IaaS, PaaS and SaaS environments</p><p>• Ability to manage a project, work to deadlines, and prioritize between competing demands</p>",
