    "description": "<p>First Wave Technology Pte. Ltd. is a global IT services company founded in 2021 and headquartered in Singapore. We specialize in helping global enterprises transform their businesses through digital transformation. First Wave operates international branch offices across Singapore, Taiwan, Jakarta, and Shanghai, etc. Our journey began with the launch of <a href=\"https://www.hicloud.sg/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Hi Cloud</a>, our first flagship Infrastructure Technology brand in Singapore. Subsequently, we successfully launched the brands of <a href=\"https://www.hiyun.com.tw/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HiYun</a> in Taiwan, and <a href=\"https://www.hicloud.co.id/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PT Hi Cloud</a> in Indonesia. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Through exceptional collaboration with leading partners and the provision of best-in-class services and solutions, First Wave plays a pivotal role in your organization’s ongoing technology strategy. We aim to help you transform your business into a catalyst for long-term organizational growth and success.</p>",
